{"tid":572990,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"婚宴現場給兒戴綠帽　公公當眾強吻兒媳婦","createTime":"2018-02-26T05:15:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-27T05:08:35.000Z","uid":1121,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"38c8276c450aade375c5bd48a93c34b861602f52","tid":572990,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T05:15:56.000Z","msg":"兒子受得了？中國江蘇鹽城市大型商場五洲國際廣場昨晚進行一場婚禮，新郎的父親竟然在喝醉酒後，當著眾賓客的面強吻兒媳婦，賓客們還起哄鼓掌。<br />\n<br />\n有網友將現場影片分享到《虎撲社區》討論區，影片中，公公摟著兒媳走台步，卻突然一把將兒媳抱住強吻，現場主持人本來還在稱讚新娘，被這一幕嚇得連聲大叫。主持人事後發文表示，「從業以來第一次覺得無所適從、無能為力，喝醉酒的公公當眾強吻兒媳新娘，救不了場。」<br />\n<br />\n影片瘋傳後也引發質疑，覺得台上「新娘」和「公公」看起來年紀沒有差很多，懷疑造假，但之後又有人po出新郎父母和新人的合照，表示舞台上的強吻確實是新娘和公公，影片中新娘看起來年紀不小可能是妝扮和拍攝的關係。還有參與婚宴的賓客也表示這件事是真的。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）"},{"pid":"da9100745bf03f5edc789cc2b661666d332ae471","tid":572990,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T05:16:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.nextmag.com.tw/breakingnews/international/386462\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nextmag.com.tw%2Fbreakingnews%2Finternational%2F386462&d=H8NQjG7nlUwDdKTXSy7tVi7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=39bae78b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.nextmag.com.tw/breakingnews/international/386462</a>"},{"pid":"c9df08c46b42e46c99718da3b4277aefe6e34301","tid":572990,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T05:17:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b92f99d838e3ca0c7ac98eaa11cc6ca33e520c4","tid":572990,"uid":1121,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T06:31:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8a644fe52e1a16b4f665db52211ff8f49d76d5b","tid":572990,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T06:35:27.000Z","msg":"父目前犯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ad6ea765a00337fdb62217861dc3df03ee03995","tid":572990,"uid"